title: Notarious
description: This week we're joined by old friend and TST alumni George "Motoman" Notaras. George shares his extensive travel log, his lust for a 427 C3 Corvette and his take on the new 718 Porsche Boxter and Cayman.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
